  <descriptions treatment="append">
    <desc lang="en-us">
        <p>Liz is a context-aware AI agent integrated into the SUSE Rancher
        Prime environment. It is designed to understand the live state of your
        clusters, namespaces, and workloads. Available as an extension, Liz
        resides within your workspace to provide real-time guidance where you
        need it.</p>
